that's why I wanted to be open about it.

1230
01:16:13,652 --> 01:16:16,656
Jesus, I'm... I'm shocked.

1231
01:16:16,822 --> 01:16:21,419
I'm... I'm shocked. I'm surprised.

1232
01:16:21,577 --> 01:16:24,877
I think I've always
been in love with him.

