He wants to move out of his place
so that we can live together.

1236
01:16:33,923 --> 01:16:37,518
I'm stunned.
I mean, I'm in a state of, uh...

1237
01:16:37,676 --> 01:16:40,896
Somebody should throw a blanket
over me. You know, I'm...

