I tend to internalize.

1246
01:17:04,203 --> 01:17:08,549
I can't express anger. That's one of the
problems I have. I grow a tumor instead.

1247
01:17:08,707 --> 01:17:11,961
Well, I told you that
I was trouble from the beginning,

1248
01:17:12,128 --> 01:17:13,721
from when we started dating.

1249
01:17:13,879 --> 01:17:16,132
So what does your analyst say?

1250
01:17:16,298 --> 01:17:19,518
Donny's in a coma.
He had a very bad acid experience.

1251
01:17:19,677 --> 01:17:23,181
Oh, that's gr... That's great.
I mean, you know...

1252
01:17:23,347 --> 01:17:25,645
I think you're making
a big mistake here.

1253
01:17:25,808 --> 01:17:26,934
Why?

1254
01:17:27,101 --> 01:17:30,105
Why? Because you... Why?
Because you're preferring Yale to me.

1255
01:17:30,271 --> 01:17:33,650
I know that sounds egotistical,
but, uh, you know...

1256
01:17:33,816 --> 01:17:37,411
This guy's been married 12 years.
