01:18:06,056 --> 01:18:08,650
Isaac, I'm sorry.
I really am. I'm really sorry.

1267
01:18:08,809 --> 01:18:11,028
Mm-mm. Oh, well, I'm...

1268
01:18:11,187 --> 01:18:13,906
I'm sorr... Where are you going?

1269
01:18:14,064 --> 01:18:16,158
- I gotta get some air.
